    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブ前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせが終わってやっと事務所に戻れたが\nもうこんな時間か……今日も朝から休む暇もなかったな",
      "startTime": 5.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10600,
          "startTime": 12.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10600,
          "startTime": 12.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！",
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季？　まだ帰っていなかったのか\nそれに、その格好は……",
      "startTime": 18.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……。これは、明日の本番に向けて\n衣装を着て練習していたんです",
      "startTime": 24.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら物音がしたので{user}さんが\n帰って来たのかと思って慌ててしまって……",
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……こんな格好ですみません",
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こんな時間まで居残り練習していたのか\n他のみんなも一緒なのか？",
      "startTime": 38.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、事務所に残っているのは私と\n{user}さんだけです",
      "startTime": 43.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、お話があるんですが\n今、お時間ありますか？",
      "startTime": 48.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば最近は忙しくて\n沙季とゆっくり話をする時間もなかったな",
      "startTime": 53.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに息抜きのお喋りでもしようか",
      "startTime": 56.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nそれで……まずは、お礼を言わせて下さい",
      "startTime": 62.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで\n期末試験と学校のクリスマス会は無事に終わりました",
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺は何もしていないよ\nうまくいったとしたら、それは沙季が頑張ったからだ",
      "startTime": 75.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "でも相談に乗ってくれたり\n息抜きに付き合ってくれたりしましたよね？",
      "startTime": 81.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの気遣いに\n私はいつも助けられていました",
      "startTime": 86.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これは感謝の気持ちです\n受け取って下さい",
      "startTime": 92.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "私からクリスマスプレゼントです\n気に入っていただけるといいのですが……",
      "startTime": 97.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、嬉しいよ。これは本かい？",
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "前にプレゼントを選ぶなら本がいいって\nアドバイスしてくれましたよね？",
      "startTime": 107.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、{user}さんのことを\n考えながら本を選んでみたんです",
      "startTime": 111.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざ俺のために選んでくれたのか\nええと、本のタイトルは……",
      "startTime": 117.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "『身だしなみに気を遣う上司に部下はついていく』と\n『残業ゼロの法則～出来る人ほど定時で帰る～』……",
      "startTime": 126.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに欠けている部分を\n補えるような本を選んでみました",
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう……普段俺がどう思われているのか\nよく分かるラインナップだよ……",
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、俺からも\nいつも頑張っている沙季にクリスマスプレゼントだ",
      "startTime": 143.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　私にですか？\nありがとうございます……あっ、それは……",
      "startTime": 151.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ショーウインドウ越しに見ていただろ？\n気に入ってもらえたかな？",
      "startTime": 159.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "はい、一目見て気に入りました\n最高のクリスマスプレゼントです！",
      "startTime": 165.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "このスノードームで誰かが笑顔になれたらって\n思ってたけど……まさか私が笑顔になるなんて……",
      "startTime": 172.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの私が\nみんなを喜ばせなきゃいけないのに……",
      "startTime": 178.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "私をこんなに喜ばせて、どういうつもりですか？",
      "startTime": 181.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "いつも沢山のものをもらっているのに\nクリスマスプレゼントまでもらえるなんて……",
      "startTime": 188.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "千紗がスノードームを今でも大切にしている気持ちが\n分かりました",
      "startTime": 194.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人からほしかった物をプレゼントされるって\nこんなに嬉しいものなんですね",
      "startTime": 199.3702471444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "え？　好きな人？",
      "startTime": 203.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_03-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ！　そういう意味じゃないですから！",
      "startTime": 206.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
